This paper discusses the next generation of mobile communication, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks and communications. Specifically, the paper focuses on the limitations of 4G networks and the new features and technologies of 5G networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses information theory (cs.IT) and communication systems (cs.COMM). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of augmented reality (cs.AR) and energy efficiency (cs.CE) in 5G networks, which are also possible sub-categories.
